snippet.title: #50easyDIY | DIY Packers beer coozie lets you be a superfan
snippet.description: Summer or winter, this easy do-it-yourself beer coozie will get you pumped up for the game, especially if you customize it for your team. This project is a part of Fresh's #50easyDIY series. See the first 25 easy DIY projects here and come back every weekday through Dec. 6
